data.description: Beautiful home in North Ridge Community in north Deland, living larger than its square footage, traditional floor plan that boasts many upgrades & features including ceilings over 10’ and crown molding throughout! Situated on nearly a HALF ACRE and with a tree -line in the backyard, privacy abounds on this gorgeous parcel with fully vinyl fenced area. As you step into the front door, a formal dining to the right & living room to the left, each filled with soft streams of sunlight flowing from their LARGE WINDOWS, provide the perfect spaces for entertaining. The heart of the home is reflected in the space beyond where Cherry Wood Laminate flooring continues and provides a comfortable gathering space in the family room that opens into the dinette. With 42’ inch Cherry Wood Cabinets lined on three separate walls, Stainless appliances, a closet pantry, and solid surface counters, the kitchen is the heart of the home. The SPLIT BEDROOM FLOOR PLAN separates the master to the left where the high ceilings continue adding to the spacious feeling of the room. Adjoining is the large  en-suite and separate HIS & HER WALK-IN CLOSETS. Additionally on the main, two secondary bedrooms share a good-sized guest bath. Upstairs, the HUGE BONUS ROOM and THIRD FULL BATH over the garage can serve as the 4th bedroom, junior master, in-law suite, man cave or playroom, making this home easily adaptable for specific and changing needs over time.  Home has NEW SOLAR SYSTEM, ROOF, and AC SYSTEM with dual zoning. Exterior has been painted as well as the interior.
